      <title>停火、OPEC+推迟，油价在清淡交投中走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对 OPEC+ 生产计划以及以色列和黎巴嫩真主党之间停火协议的持久性存在不确定性，油价在假期后清淡的交易中走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 23:29:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数创下今年最佳月份；收益率下降：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市在交易时段结束时上涨，而美国国债收益率全线下跌。外界猜测当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将缓和其最极端的贸易政策，导致美元创下三个月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 22:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
